{"tid":1888191,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中國發現抗疫秘訣：更改「確診」定義，確診病例數目立即大降","createTime":"2020-02-20T04:57:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T05:17:08.000Z","uid":48040,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"6d01f55de99e81249b525b98e3df92b4b9be6aed","tid":1888191,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T04:57:37.000Z","msg":"今日湖北每日確診病例突然從近2000宗急跌至349宗，莫非疫情突然受控？<br />\n當然唔係啦，係因為中國剛剛修改了確診標準。<br />\n按照之前標準，湖北省內病人如果肺部被感染，但核酸測試為陰性，照樣會被視為「確診」，所以有一日突然新增1.5萬宗。<br />\n但昨日中國再次修改標準，這類「陰性」但肺部感染的湖北病人不再視為「確診」，所以昨日湖北「確診」病人只有349例。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3073715\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3073715&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OffilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=db68b70b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3073715&h=c5c9a40c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3073715</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.caixin.com/2020-02-19/101517559.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.caixin.com%2F2020-02-19%2F101517559.html&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OffilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=9cd180e6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.caixin.com/2020-02-19/101517559.html</a>"},{"pid":"8ed2fd56b722d178daf421a6e6e54ec9ee67ac9d","tid":1888191,"uid":169195,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:00:03.000Z","msg":"任佢玩啦<br />\n佢叫返哂D人出黎傳到滅國咪好"},{"pid":"9ba75d6bfb5ca3c1aa781d3f7bd7ed6231ea10e9","tid":1888191,"uid":46933,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:02:07.000Z","msg":"一換左人就改正標準<br />\n話上一手隱瞞疫情<br />\n之後自己又改返原先標準<br />\n自己抗疫成功"},{"pid":"839570924a02d686a2af935d5f3d84135664cbbe","tid":1888191,"uid":226955,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:04:53.000Z","msg":"人哋要復工嘛，唔壓低個數字點氹到你去返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class