d7079d2d461a5351c95be134344","tid":1888191,"uid":810,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:09:26.000Z","msg":"死左唔計，醫唔到唔計，唔應診唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be84c0dfde05266e80ec6f5aa7de32b7360168f","tid":1888191,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:09:37.000Z","msg":"哇真係自殺式"},{"pid":"4dca2c29a47f3cb1ccc1fae2d725337f3b434571","tid":1888191,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:09:52.000Z","msg":"鴕鳥政策<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d30407381a63b24ba04d8977c1c63358ca6b351","tid":1888191,"uid":68463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:11:04.000Z","msg":"做得好"},{"pid":"65da828e5604cd5edaed76f1b5d2c809c6cbb52e","tid":1888191,"uid":121580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:11:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pNbjOrR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpNbjOrR.jpg&h=284fe568&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bac03cf27d5de78d3525b5e6b0edd2b06c4aed9e","tid":1888191,"uid":76310,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:13:00.000Z","msg":"如何才能確診武漢肺炎？<br />\n<br />\n1.需要有齊武漢肺炎所有病徵<br />\n2.需要官方認可醫生確認<br />\n3.需要官方認可醫院確認<br />\n4.需要使用官方認可的檢測方法下確診<br />\n5.需在十四天內發病<br />\n6.需要發燒高於38度<br />\n7.需要在官方指定隔離地點十四天內發病<br />\n8.需要確認與確診者有直接接觸<br />\n9.不能有其他病<br />\n<br />\nn. 即使有齊以上徵狀條件 如果中央政府不承認你有武漢肺炎 你就沒有確診"},{"pid":"a555da9bcc6a1c2fef590e3bdcac9b1145d37abf","tid":1888191,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13a1ed1157f7c8211510714517a69f982a75874b","tid":1888191,"uid":49784,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:07:47.000Z","msg":"又咪死，真係改個數字就抗疫成功，一早改啦<br />\n<br />\n咁改法，全面復工，之後都係死路一條<br />\n<br />\n中國人真係奇怪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:13:18.000Z","msg":"最緊要保住自己個頭頂烏紗，其他人死關我咩事?"},{